{
  "text": "On the other hand, transdermal-ART gels (Andro-Gel TM , Testim TM , and Androderm TM ) are reported to increase serum fT levels to reach the normal range within one hour after administration and maintain them within that range thereafter. Testosterone gels (Andro-Gel TM and Testim TM ), which are applied to the patient's body surface every day, maintain serum levels of tT and fT within the normal range [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] and also maintain serum FSH and LH at a constant level.",
